Cyberpunk style: A menacing digital wolf made of glowing orange and red code fragments stalks through a neon-lit cityscape at night, its eyes burning with malicious intent as it hunts among streams of flowing data packets visualized as small luminous orbs traveling along fiber-optic cables. In the foreground, a translucent protective dome shield with hexagonal patterns pulses with electric blue energy, deflecting the predator. The shield emanates from a sleek black server tower that stands like a monolith, its surface covered in intricate circuit patterns. Rain falls through holographic advertisements, creating reflections on wet chrome streets. The atmosphere is tense, with deep purple shadows contrasting against hot pink and cyan highlights, capturing the eternal battle between vulnerability and protection in the digital realm.
